Name: Shaving Gel
Description: King Kind Shaving gel provides an easy professional shaving that softens the beard and prevents skin irritation. Compared to shaving creams, it allows faster removal with less amount and it provides transparency so you can see where the razor blades have already passed through. KK Shaving Gel creates a layer between the blade and your skin, shielding it from cuts, nicks, razor burns, leaving skin fresh, smooth and moisturised. Perfect for professional barber use. Dispenser provides easily the product in-hand avoiding contamination of the product. • Easy application: dispenses product in-hand • Great Visibility: clear gel for transparent visibility during shaving • Comfort: goes on smoothly and provides a slick surface for comfort shaving • Precision: softens the beard, goes on clear for a clean, close and comfortable shave • Moisturing formula: non-foaming moisturing formula leaves skin fresh and soft. Suitable for sensitive skin • No razor clogs formula: The rich non-foaming formula won’t clog your razor providing a slick surface that prevents razor burn, nicks and cuts.   Product Short Description: Brand: King Kind Shaving Gel Category: Shaving products Type: Shaving gel Scent: fresh, citrus notes Size:500 ml

Name: Hot wax
Description: INSTRUCTIONS FOR USE:   Use a sharp object and break the quantity of wax that you want to use for your application. Warm the wax inside a heating device until it melts. Prepare properly the skin for the hair removal with a specialized product or use talc powder to remove any potential greasiness on the area to be depilated. Using a spatula, spread a thin layer of wax on the area you wish to depilate in the direction of hair growth. Let it dry. Pull it away quickly in the opposite direction of hair growth with a movement parallel to the skin. A second application of wax can also be done in the opposite direction of hair growth and pulled away in the direction of hair growth. Use a specialized post depilation care product to calm the skin after the hair removal.    PRECAUTIONS: Before applying the hot wax on the area to be depilated, check if its temperature is bearable for your skin. Do not apply on irritated skin, wounds, or skin affected with pathologies. Avoid contact with eyes. In case of contact with eyes rinse immediately with water for at least 10 minutes. Keep out of the reach of children. STORAGE CONDITIONS: always prefer to store the product in a cool and dry place, and avoid exposing it to direct sunlight. Storage temperature, preferably 4-25 degrees Celsius.    INGREDIENTS: Glyceryl Rosinate, Cera Microcristallina, Paraffinum Liquidum, Cera Alba, CI 77499.
